grid.text: First pine: L. turn. Forward pointing.

captions.transcription: [JIUTAI] Ika ni ya Munechika choku no tsurugi.
Ika ni ya Munechika choku no tsurugi,

captions.translation: The appointed time for forging is known!
captions.transcription: utsubeki jisetsu wa kōku ni shireri.
captions.japaneseScript: 打つべき時節は虚空に知れり。

captions.translation: Trust and have faith!  Only trust!
captions.transcription: Tanome ya, tanome ya, tada tanome.
